PENN NATIONAL INSURANCE COMPANY, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
GROUP C COMMUNICATIONS, INC., Defendant-Respondent. G.M. Sign, Inc., Individually and on Behalf of a Certified Class as Judgment Creditors of Group C Communications, Inc., Intervenor-Respondent. Penn National Insurance Company, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Group C. Communications, Inc., Defendant-Respondent. G.M. Sign, Inc., Individually and on Behalf of a Certified Class as Judgment Creditors of Group C Communications, Inc., Intervenor-Respondent. C-385 September Term 2018
081828 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 11, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-0754/0808-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
